  "original_title": "\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf, \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc7 \u0b8e\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0ba3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1 -  \u0bb0\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0bae\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb0",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dulles President, Sajith Prime Minister is our consensus - Ranjith Mathuma Bandara",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Our agreement is that Dulles will be the President and Sajith will be the Prime Minister. According to it, the all-party government is united and we are taking necessary programs to solve the basic problems of the people quickly.",
        "Parliament adjourned on Tuesday (19) after the nomination of the presidential candidate was tabled.",
        "Our leader Sajith Premadasa took a step back at a time when he should have dedicated himself to the country and withdrew from running as a presidential candidate with the sole aim of solving the problem facing the country. He also said that Sajith Premadasave proposed the opposition MP Tanus Alakkaperuma as the presidential candidate.",
        "At this time, a journalist asked whether you came to this decision with the agreement of President Dulles and Prime Minister Sajid, of course, we are discussing on that basis.",
        "We are merging all the parties to form an all-party government. We have started work on the initial plans of an all-party government a week ago.",
        "Now we have started the program that is being carried out by all together, which is expected by the people. He said that our plan is to form a cabinet that includes all parties",
        "Will you get the support of the Tamil National Federation during this? To the question raised by a journalist",
        "We are confident that we will get the support of the Tamil National Federation when he answers. We are ready to discuss with them regarding their demands. He also said that they will never support a failing government."
      ],
